reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars YOUR PHONE WILL SURVIVE ANY DROP
reviews.reviewText: i've had this phone case for almost a year and its saved my phone from many drops including falling off a roller coaster. only the case has some tiny marks and my screen protector in front was scratched but the back... perfectly fine. This is worth the money its very solid and not too bulky or heavy for the protection it offers. I would recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 8, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is pretty good. 👍🏼
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my iPhone 11 it fits perfectly. I liked that it’s clear, so my iPhone color shows through (it’s the lavender/purple one).It’s pretty sturdy, while being slim enough as if you almost didn’t have a case on your phone, and allows for easy use if all your buttons (including the back of the phone icon that turns your phone on).It’s easy to put on and take off, so I can clean my phone every so often, and the case itself.I’ve dropped my phone a couple times (not hard, but still a drop) on hardwood floors and it withstand the impact, no damage to any part of my iPhone. It has a slight lip on the screen side (just its thickness), which keeps the front off the counter if you were placing it face down, hence protect it if it fell that way. Same with the back camera.Over time it will probably yellow a bit, but I’ve had it a while now, and it’s still looking great, so I think you’ll get a new phone before you need to change the case out. 😉I only wish it came with a carry or clip on case, like other otter boxes, as I don’t like to put phone in my pocket, so I’d rather clip to my belt or my handbag.Being clear, it can work for anyone, gender, age etc as its basically just a cover for your phone and whatever color your phone is, that’s what you’ll see.Thumbs up for me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Amended review after a year of use
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I have been a fan of Otterbox/Lifeproof phone cases for years and got one for my new iPhone 13 promax. It held up wonderfully, however, the edges of the clear case started to turn yellow after about six months.When my husband bought his iPhone 14, we transitioned to MagSafe charging. This particular case does not support the MagSafe charging, in that it will not stick to the vertical chargers. I replaced this case for one that advertised that it would not yellow and is compatible with MagSafe charging. Unfortunately it was not Otterbox/Lifeproof.

reviews.reviewText: This OtterBox case is my favorite! It is lightweight and has a great grip. reviews.reviewText: OtterBox Prefix is a great choice. Case is slim & durable. Love it in clear. Encouraging everybody to scroll through the used options when shopping on Amazon before making your purchases (for most things). Very satisfied with my order. The box was slightly smashed but product is excellent.No damage and saved some money choosing used.

reviews.reviewTitle: Best slim case I've ever used
reviews.reviewText: I can't take a photo since it's on my phone, but this is by far the highest quality relatively low profile case I've ever had on a phone. It protects just enough while looking good and being flexible and able to be removed when necessary. Works with my glass screen protector too without restricting it or touching it. It has a subtle, though firm, silicone feel on the side as well for easy grip, and the clear window in the back means you see the factory look of the phone.Highly recommended!
Llego a tiempo de acuerdo a Amazon.Recibí un excelente case para mi iPhone 11. Lo único que no venía en su caja original pero seguro que es original.

I order one of these every time I upgrade my phone. It’s not bulky and it offers great protection. I drop my phone a fair amount and it has never suffered any damage. The case I got is sparkly so it looks quite nice on my blue phone.

reviews.reviewTitle: Kept my phone safe, however only used it for a few months…
reviews.reviewText: I used this case for about 4-5 months. But once it started getting dirty I bought a different case. Otterbox is a great brand, however, I didn’t drop this phone when the side trim started breaking, which was another factor that made me buy a new case. Only had this one for a few months.
